snippet.title: OMUT - Official Trailer | Six One Indie Showcase
snippet.description: Embark upon a mysterious quest to find a woman from your dreams along with an wise-cracking yet ominous companion, battling through strange and terrifying entities on the sinister journey into the murky depths of the Red Abyss. Take a look at the surreal world of OMUT in this trailer for the game, coming to PC.
